name: Resonance
description:
NFT comes with Unique 1/1, Museum Quality Photograph, Size Variable (Max: 245 x 245 cm [96 x 96 inches]) by Christy Lee Rogers. 

Christy Lee Rogers beat 274,000 entries to win the Sony World Open Photography Award. Apple commissioned her to make 12 photographs and made a film about her which they released on Instagram on New Years Eve. Lavazza commissioned Christy for the cover of their legendary calendar and CNN said "Christy Lee Rogers is one of the most prominent artists in the field of underwater photography. Her images push the boundaries of reality and can be easily mistaken for paintings."
